data.title: Original photograph of Julie Andrews and Blake Edwards on the set of Darling Lili, 1970 by Julie Andrews, Blake Edwards (subjects): (1960)
data.meta_description: N.p., N.p. - 1960 - Vintage borderless photograph of actress Julie Andrews and her husband, director Blake Edwards, on the set of "Darling Lili" in 1970. Edwards and Andrews were married for over four decades, from 1969 until Edwards' death in 2010. 7.75 x 9.25 inches. Near Fine. - Original photograph of Julie Andrews and Blake Edwards on the set of Darling Lili, 1970
